b.com</a><br />\nTG id: <a href=\"http://t.me/hkcpgdb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkcpgdb&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebdjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=24a69456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkcpgdb</a> <br />\nTG Channel: <a href=\"http://t.me/thzforlisten2me\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fthzforlisten2me&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebdjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=3627754a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/thzforlisten2me</a><br />\n報料 Email: hkcpgdb@protonmail.com<br />\n<br />\n懲罰 Link 求懲罰<br />\n你既支持 我既動力<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcpgdb.com/donate.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcpgdb.com%2Fdonate.html&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebdjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=87203227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcpgdb.com/donate.html</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T04:16:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">會唔會考慮放埋資料入去？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_7j-Ynup6BM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_7j-Ynup6BM&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebdjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=b4514232\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_7j-Ynup6BM</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/library-19_1oR46_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Flibrary-19_1oR46_1200x0.png&h=3f0a16fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新聞自由並非必然，一些專權國家就往往以資訊封鎖的方式阻止人民接觸真相，甚至傷害講出真相的人。為了以更生動的方式推廣，「無國界記者」（RSF）與專門以電腦遊戲《Minecraft》進行設計的工作室 BlockWorks 合作，興建了一個虛擬圖書館 The Uncensored Library，記載了俄羅斯、越南、沙特阿拉伯、墨西哥以及埃及的新聞封鎖事件，讓玩家和網民「進館」細閱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/89489260_504958376817304_7576411508024803328_n_72ZOj_1200x0.png\" /><br />\n<br />\nBlockworks 找來了 16 個國家的 24 名 Minecraft 高手，用了超過 250 小時、1,250 萬 Minecraft 磚頭才建好這個虛擬圖書館。圖書館設有一個圓拱形大廳，訪客可以經大廳前往 6 個區域。在各個區域裡，訪客可以點擊書架上的書本，觀看那些被封鎖的新聞資訊。除了文章之後，還會有記者的語音檔可以收聽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/89731624_2848164971946903_1448047489406992384_n_PltFW_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F89731624_2848164971946903_1448047489406992384_n_PltFW_1200x0.png&h=520dbfe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/89681558_244826466543607_2791960138058039296_n_yzRmD_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F89681558_244826466543607_2791960138058039296_n_yzRmD_1200x0.png&h=b37f5409&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果是 Minecraft 的玩家，他們可以透過官方網站來下載圖書館，並在《Minecraft》遊戲中以單人模式進入地圖。除此之外，他們也可以選擇直接連線，在線上伺服器與其他玩家交流。但如果不是 Minecraft 的玩家，無國界記者也準備了網頁版的圖書館給網民瀏覽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/89352175_248633636150942_1170845678738341888_n_TAVmP_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F89352175_248633636150942_1170845678738341888_n_TAVmP_1200x0.png&h=3f094323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRSF 表示，希望透過 Minecraft 這個遊戲，讓世上每一個人，都可以知道新聞和資訊封鎖的問題。另外，他們特別關注年輕人如果受到資訊封鎖影響，將無法表達他們的意見，所以組織特別聚焦在電腦遊戲上，讓他們接收到獨立的資訊。RSF 表示，他們會不斷增加虛擬圖書館的館藏。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/90030207_820600528459361_1554347182658682880_n_kMMo2_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F90030207_820600528459361_1554347182658682880_n_kMMo2_1200x0.png&h=55d9c3e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T15:57:09.000Z","msg":"點先放到"},{"pid":"5693fc5b7e773a2708c705aca38040c329072273","tid":1928613,"uid":254114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T17:00:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f46d9635fc650da5f3343e8f7d29a553d87427c","tid":1928613,"uid":27411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T17:05:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cafb9cf6f810715b9f018cdc24eebc6ed8d3f5c","tid":1928613,"uid":28446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T17:11:42.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n香港警察=黃賭毒犯罪集團"},{"pid":"6a75d29426edc2aaa31a749b801cb24ea76df696","tid":1928613,"uid":254114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T19:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8edeabadb8aefe5dd05a159229730ac70c858b31","tid":1928613,"uid":24572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c23084c545a3e5b8b0bbe8f2eaf02a7e17fc639e","tid":1928613,"uid":252591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f9adf6d1c72d63941675fe4f71dccc59e285587","tid":1928613,"uid":292497,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:37:03.000Z","msg":"陳雅倫<br />\n鄧炳強<br />\n謝振美<br />\n夠薑出黎隻秋 香蕉糖<br />\n唔撚洗show pass<br />\n遊乃強"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:02:05.000Z","msg":"陳雅倫 good"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T20:09:14.000Z","msg":"依個？姓鍾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZozJmq1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZozJmq1.png&h=84a081e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e4026ee8b26e32691b102e375e355eeee62632d","tid":1928613,"uid":196701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1f2f0451d68d6f13b6cf175b70c942b47076e87","tid":1928613,"uid":154106,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:37:40.000Z","msg":"警隊黎明 吳樂俊 脫光光俾人影淫照有傷風化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T22:20:11.000Z","msg":"呢個我記得，係咪叫雞王鄭文𠎀"},{"pid":"45864e68c6975789ab8d334cb3668b254e8dea67","tid":1928613,"uid":337052,"like":0,"